Code.Terraform:
```hcl
resource "azuread_conditional_access_policy" "<example_resource_name>" {
  display_name = "<example_resource_name>"
  state        = "enabled" # Critical: must be enabled (not report-only) to enforce

  conditions {
    users {
      included_users = ["All"] # Critical: target all users
    }
    applications {
      included_applications = ["All"] # Critical: apply to all cloud apps
    }
  }

  session_controls {
    continuous_access_evaluation = true # Critical: enable CAE
  }
}
```
